I have taken A Very Potter Musical (in ISO format) and paired it with A Very Potter Sequel (Act 1 and Act 2, in .avi) for easier viewing pleasure. The volume is low in places, since it is a filmed play, so speakers may be necessary.


This is my first torrent, so I hope you like it. Enjoy the plays!
